OL,3,CTaxi driver jailed for encouraging
OL,4,Cviolent disorder via chat rooms
OL,6,FA man who set up a channel on a
OL,7,Fmessaging platform described as a
OL,8,F"catalyst" for violent disorder has
OL,9,Fbeen jailed.
OL,11,FAndrew McIntyre, from Rufford near
OL,12,FOrmskirk, founded a Telegram channel
OL,13,Fcalled "Southport Wake Up" in the
OL,14,Fimmediate aftermath of the knife
OL,15,Fattack in Southport on 29 July 2024.
OL,17,FThe channel was later identified by
OL,18,Fthe group Hope Not Hate as a "catalyst
OL,19,Ffor and origin of a series of posts"
OL,20,Fconcerning incidents of violence
OL,21,Facross the town and further afield.
