OL,6,FSocial media platform Telegram is a
OL,7,Fmessaging app which primarily allows
OL,8,Fusers to communicate through one-on-
OL,9,Fone chats, group chats, voice and
OL,10,Fvideo calls, and channels.
OL,12,FLiverpool Crown Court heard the 39-
OL,13,Fyear-old shared content on the channel
OL,14,Ffrom a site called Tommy Robinson/
OL,15,F Britain First/ For Britain about a
OL,16,Fprotest in Southport on 30 July.
OL,18,FHe also posted a map after adding:
OL,19,F"Mosque at the top of Hart St."
