OL,4,Cviolent disorder via chat rooms
OL,6,FIn a later post he wrote: "Rise Up
OL,7,FEnglish Lads. 8pm tomorrow St Luke's
OL,8,FRd Southport."
OL,10,FHours before violence broke out in
OL,11,FSouthport on 30 July, he posted a
OL,12,F"clear threat to police", writing:
OL,13,F"Message to All...Stand in our way,
OL,14,Feven if you're just doing your job...
OL,15,Fprepare to fall."
OL,17,FAnother user responded: "We'll get to
OL,18,Fthe mosque and rip it f****** down."
