OL,3,CTaxi driver jailed for encouraging
OL,4,Cviolent disorder via chat rooms
OL,6,FSentencing him, Judge Neil Flewitt KC
OL,7,Fsaid the defendant was "prominent"
OL,8,Famong people responsible for spreading
OL,9,Fmisinformation following the Southport
OL,10,Fattack.
OL,12,FHe said: "You were motivated by racial
OL,13,Fhatred.
OL,15,F"I have no doubt your actions
OL,16,Fencouraged many people to plan and
OL,17,Fthen to commit offences of both
OL,18,Fviolent disorder and criminal damage."
