OL,3,CTaxi driver jailed for encouraging
OL,4,Cviolent disorder via chat rooms
OL,6,FHe said the offence was aggravated
OL,7,Fbecause it was motivated by racial
OL,8,Fhostility and involved attacks on
OL,9,Fpolice officers.
OL,11,FArthur Gibson, prosecuting, said the
OL,12,Fcase involved a "sinister aspect" of
OL,13,Fviolence which took place in parts of
OL,14,Fthe UK last summer.
OL,16,FHe said: "It is the prosecution case
OL,17,Fthat many of these seats of disorder
OL,18,Fwere not simply spontaneous, or that
OL,19,Fpersons coincidentally simply decided
OL,20,Fto turn up and take part.
OL,26,@tD@QOUtD@aO]xD@JOU
