OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F392A1736190319
OL,3,CTaxi driver jailed for encouraging
OL,4,Cviolent disorder via chat rooms
OL,6,F"It is the Crown's case that others,
OL,7,Fto a greater or lesser degree,
OL,8,Fparticipated in the organisation,
OL,9,Fencouragement and incitement of such
OL,10,Fgatherings, which resulted in the
OL,11,Fdisorder.
OL,13,F"It is the Crown's case that one such
OL,14,Fperson is the defendant."
OL,16,FThe court was told McIntyre's phone
OL,17,Fwas in the area of St Luke's Road in
OL,18,FSouthport at 7pm on July 30, and the
OL,19,Fcar in which he was later arrested was
OL,20,Falso in the area when the disorder
OL,21,Ftook place.
