OL,6,FThe day after the disorder, McIntyre
OL,7,Fposted: "Well done last night lads, to
OL,8,Fall you heavy hitters.
OL,10,F"Are you ready for Round 2???...
OL,11,FLiverpool Mosque, West Derby Road,
OL,12,FFriday 8pm."
OL,14,FMcIntyre was working as a taxi driver
OL,15,Fwhen he was intercepted by police in
OL,16,FLiverpool on August 8 and arrested, Mr
OL,17,FGibson said.
