OL,6,FA knife was found hidden in the boot
OL,7,Fof his car and, when his home was
OL,8,Fsearched, officers found weapons and a
OL,9,Fcopy of Hitler's Mein Kampf, the court
OL,10,Fheard.
OL,12,FThe defendant was originally charged
OL,13,Fwith encouraging murder, after posting
OL,14,Fa link to a YouTube video of the Home
OL,15,FSecretary with the caption: "We're
OL,16,Fgoing to hang this woman and her
OL,17,Fassociates."
