OL,6,FMr Gibson said the decision was taken
OL,7,Fby the Crown Prosecution Service (CPS)
OL,8,Fnot to pursue the charge to trial
OL,9,Fbecause of "evidential issues"
OL,10,Fconcerning whether the defendant
OL,11,Factually believed the act would be
OL,12,Fcarried out.
OL,14,FThe defendant followed proceedings on
OL,15,Fa videolink from HMP Liverpool, where
OL,16,Fhe has been remanded in custody, while
OL,17,Fhis parents looked on from the public
OL,18,Fgallery of the courtroom.
OL,26,@qD@LOUqD@^O]
