OL,6,FJulian Nutter, defending, said: "His
OL,7,Fparents are horrified that he is in
OL,8,Fthis predicament.
OL,10,F"He is a man of previous good
OL,11,Fcharacter and has never come to the
OL,12,Fattention of the police before."
OL,14,FAmong character references were
OL,15,Fletters to Judge Neil Flewitt KC from
OL,16,FMcIntyre's parents and a family
OL,17,Ffriend, the court heard.
