OL,6,FMr Nutter said: "Those who have spoken
OL,7,Fon his behalf describe somebody who is
OL,8,Fvery different from what we have heard
OL,9,Ffrom the prosecution about him."
OL,11,FMcIntyre, who pleaded guilty to
OL,12,Fencouraging violent disorder and
OL,13,Fpossession of a knife, was sentenced
OL,14,Fto seven-and-a-half-years in jail.
